04:26.900 --> 04:28.767
-Is that a real staple?
-ROSS: That is a real staple.

04:28.833 --> 04:29.833
SANKEY: Okay, now watch.

04:29.900 --> 04:31.833
A little heat, this is again
the magic of fire.

04:31.900 --> 04:35.100
