Is there a top hat?

37:51.700 --> 37:52.767
You have a top hat.

37:52.833 --> 37:54.233
Could you come up here please?
Right up here, yeah.

37:54.300 --> 37:55.733
Bring your top hat with you
right up here, please.

37:55.800 --> 37:56.967
Thank you so much.

37:57.867 --> 37:59.567
-What is your name, please?
-Kat.

37:59.633 --> 38:01.000
Hello, Kat, my name is Penn.

38:01.133 --> 38:03.267
This is Teller right here.
Kat.

38:03.467 --> 38:05.200
And, Kat, take a look at that top hat,
huh?

38:05.300 --> 38:07.567
May I borrow the top hat back
for a moment, please, Kat?

38:07.633 --> 38:08.633
Thank you so much.

38:08.700 --> 38:11.233
And now, Kat, did you get a chance
to fold it up like this?

38:11.300 --> 38:12.600
-I did.
-And you opened it up like that,

38:12.667 --> 38:14.733
you did all that?
Did you look around on the inside?

38:14.800 --> 38:15.933
-Yes, I did.
-It's completely empty,

38:16.000 --> 38:18.567
'cause I'm gonna show this to the camera,
